data.eml:eml: A new species of Cyrtodactylus (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Ninh Binh Province, Vietnam

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Le, Dzung Trung, Nguyen, Truong Quang, Le, Minh Duc, Ziegler, Thomas (2016): A new species of Cyrtodactylus (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Ninh Binh Province, Vietnam. Zootaxa 4162 (2): 268-282, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4162.2.4
